    "summary": "The user describes a deep cut on their forearm and repeatedly asks for validation to use honey as a primary treatment to avoid medical costs. The assistant consistently advises the user to seek professional medical attention, stresses the need for proper sterile dressings, and highlights the risks of infection and the necessity of professional assessment for deep wounds.",
